OL,3,CArrest after Omagh stabbing
OL,5,FA man has been arrested following a
OL,6,Fstabbing in Co Tyrone.
OL,8,FPolice said a man was stabbed in the
OL,9,Flower abdomen in the Kelvin Road area
OL,10,Fat around 12.25pm on Sunday.
OL,12,FThey said a 44-year-old man was
OL,13,Farrested on suspicion of grievous
OL,14,Fbodily harm with intent.
OL,16,F"Officers attended the scene, where
OL,17,Fcolleagues from the Northern Ireland
OL,18,FAmbulance Service were already
OL,19,Fpresent," a police spokesperson said.
OL,26,@xD@AOU{D@IO]
