OL,3,CArrest after Omagh stabbing
OL,5,F"The male was then taken on to
OL,6,Fhospital for treatment to his injuries.
OL,8,F"A 44-year-old man was arrested on
OL,9,Fsuspicion of grievous bodily harm with
OL,10,Fintent.
OL,12,F"He remains in police custody at this
OL,13,Ftime."
OL,15,FThey added: "Our inquiries are ongoing
OL,16,Fand anyone with information, including
OL,17,FCCTV, ring-doorbell or other footage,
OL,18,Fis asked to contact detectives on the
OL,19,F101 number."
